The '''''Dark Tide'' duology''' was written by [[Michael A. Stackpole]] and contained the novels ''[[The New Jedi Order: Dark Tide I: Onslaught]]'' and ''[[The New Jedi Order: Dark Tide II: Ruin]]''. The duology is part of the [[Star Wars: The New Jedi Order|New Jedi Order series]].

It was originally going to be a trilogy, but ''[[The New Jedi Order: Dark Tide: Siege]]'' was removed.

In June of 2000 both novels in the duology were published in single volume Hardcover exclusively by the [[Science Fiction Book Club]].

